f(x,y) = 1/\pi r^2
x^2+y^2 \leq r^2
-\sqrt{1-x^2}
\sqrt{1-x^2}
\int \frac{x}{\pi r^2} dx
E[X]
E[Y]
X
Y
E[X]=E[Y]
E[XY]=\int_{X}\int_{Y} xyf(x,y)\mathrm{dy\,dx}=\int_{-r}^{r}\int_{-\sqrt{r^2-x^2}}^{\sqrt{r^2-x^2}}\frac{xy}{\pi r^2} \mathrm{dy\,dx} 
E[X]=\int_{X}xf_X(x)dx=\int_{X}x\left(\int_{Y}f(x,y)dy\right)dx=\int_{-r}^{r}x\left(\int_{-\sqrt{r^2-x^2}}^{\sqrt{r^2-x^2}}\frac{1}{\pi r^2}dy\right)dx
